---
layout: base
title: "Submit a Tip"
description: Share a news tip with The Freethinking Times. Anonymous submissions welcome.
permalink: /tips/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-20);">
  <div class="container--prose">

    <header class="page-header">
      <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol class="breadcrumbs__list">
          <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a class="breadcrumbs__link" href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a class="breadcrumbs__link" href="/contact/">Contact</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumbs__item breadcrumbs__item--current" aria-current="page">Tip Line</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">Tip Line</h1>
      <p class="page-header__lede">
        Have information we should know about? Read the security notes below before choosing how to reach us.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">

      <p>We are interested in tips related to: religious institutions and their public influence, church-state violations, suppression of scientific information, censorship of secular voices, and abuses of power conducted under religious authority.</p>

      <div class="callout callout--warning" style="margin: var(--space-6) 0; padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5); background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--text-md); line-height: var(--leading-normal);">
        <p style="font-family: var(--font-ui); font-size: var(--text-xs); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);">Before you send anything</p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);"><strong>This form is not anonymous.</strong> Submissions flow through <a href="https://web3forms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Web3Forms</a> (a third-party handler that logs IP addresses for spam prevention) and <a href="https://www.hcaptcha.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hCaptcha</a> (which fingerprints your browser). Your connection metadata — IP, user agent, timing — is visible to those services.</p>
        <p style="margin: 0;">If your tip could put you at risk (employer retaliation, legal exposure, physical danger), do <em>not</em> use this form. Use one of the safer channels below instead.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 id="safer-channels">For sensitive tips</h2>
      <p>If anonymity genuinely matters, pick one of these out-of-band channels:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Tor Browser + an anonymous email account.</strong> Create a <a href="https://proton.me/mail" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ProtonMail</a> or <a href="https://tutanota.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tuta</a> account over Tor, send from there to <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>. Never log into that inbox over your normal connection.</li>
        <li><strong>Signal, on a burner.</strong> Install <a href="https://signal.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Signal</a> on a phone not associated with your legal name (prepaid SIM, or WiFi-only + <a href="https://signal.org/support/articles/360007318691-Signal-registration-with-a-non-US-or-EU-number" target="_blank" rel="noopener">registration tips</a>) and message us to request a Signal contact.</li>
        <li><strong>Physical mail.</strong> Printed, no return address, dropped from a mailbox that isn&rsquo;t your own, to our editorial address on the <a href="/masthead/">masthead</a>.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The form below is fine for lower-risk tips &mdash; public-record leads, stories we should be covering, general corrections, church/state issues with no personal retaliation risk. Think of it as a quick-send channel, not a whistleblower pipeline.</p>

      <p>If you do use the form, you don&rsquo;t need to provide your name or email. If you do, we will not publish your identity without your explicit written consent. You can also send tips via <a href="/contact/">our contact form</a>.</p>

      <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="w3f" style="margin: var(--space-6) 0;">
        <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="{{ site.forms.accessKey }}">
        <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Anonymous tip, {{ site.title }}">
        <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="{{ site.url }}/thank-you/">
        <input type="hidden" name="from_name" value="{{ site.title }} Tip Line">
        <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" class="visually-hidden" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">

        <div class="w3f__group">
          <label class="w3f__label" for="tip-topic">What is this about?</label>
          <select class="w3f__select" name="topic" id="tip-topic">
            <option value="Church-state violation">Church-state violation</option>
            <option value="Institutional misconduct">Institutional misconduct</option>
            <option value="Censorship">Censorship or suppression</option>
            <option value="Science denial">Science denial in policy</option>
            <option value="Discrimination">Religious discrimination</option>
            <option value="Story lead">General story lead</option>
            <option value="Other">Other</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__group">
          <label class="w3f__label" for="tip-message">Your tip <span class="w3f__required">*</span></label>
          <span class="w3f__hint" id="tip-msg-hint">Be as specific as you can. Who, what, where, when. Names, dates, and documents help us investigate.</span>
          <textarea class="w3f__textarea" name="message" id="tip-message" rows="8" required aria-required="true" aria-describedby="tip-msg-hint" maxlength="5000" data-dictation></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__group">
          <label class="w3f__label" for="tip-sources">Supporting links or references <span class="w3f__optional">(optional)</span></label>
          <span class="w3f__hint" id="tip-sources-hint">Links to public records, news articles, social media posts, or other evidence</span>
          <textarea class="w3f__textarea" name="sources" id="tip-sources" rows="3" aria-describedby="tip-sources-hint" maxlength="2000"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="w3f__row">
          <div class="w3f__group">
            <label class="w3f__label" for="tip-name">Your name <span class="w3f__optional">(optional)</span></label>
            <input class="w3f__input" type="text" name="name" id="tip-name" autocomplete="off">
          </div>
          <div class="w3f__group">
            <label class="w3f__label" for="tip-email">Email <span class="w3f__optional">(optional, only if you want us to follow up)</span></label>
            <input class="w3f__input" type="email" name="email" id="tip-email" autocomplete="off">
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="w3f__submit">Send Tip</button>
        <p class="w3f__privacy">Submitted through Web3Forms (which logs IPs for spam prevention) to our editorial inbox. We never sell or share tips. Your identity will never be published without your explicit written consent. For true anonymity, use one of the <a href="#safer-channels">safer channels above</a>.</p>
      </form>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
